Program: Start the Week
Title: 20/07/2009
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00lny46
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 20 Jul 2009
Andrew Marr sets the cultural agenda for the week. He is joined by the former cabinet minister James Purnell on the future of the Left in Britain, the writer Hanif Kureishi on the theatre adaptation of his novel The Black Album, doctor David Haslam on a cultural history of obesity and Tristram Stuart on wastefulness. Show less